description: Hufvudstaden AB engages in the ownership, development, and management of commercial properties. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 140 full-time employees.  The firm's principal activities include investments in office and retail properties. Hufvudstaden AB properties are mainly situated in the central business districts of Stockholm and Gothenburg in Sweden. The firm operates through three business divisions: Stockholm City East, Stockholm City West and Gothenburg, as well as three support functions: Accounting/Finance, Property Development and Human Resources. The firm carries on its parking operations through the subsidiary Parkaden AB. Hufvudstaden AB’s subsidiaries include AB Citypalatset,, Fastighetsaktiebolaget Medusa and AB Nordiska Kompaniet, among others.
name: Hufvudstaden AB
